commentary: Mohammed Shami to Hetmyer, SIX runs Hetmyer has his hands aloft and salutes to the change room. What a way to bring up a century. What a hundred this has been. This is Hetmyer's third in ODI cricket. Full and outside off, 140ks, Hetmyer stays leg-side of the ball and hoists it up and over the covers. Goes all the way. Kohli applauds Hetmyer
